pantron. We have arrived. The war on cybertron is almost over. Magmnatron is 
looking for a way to retreat back to past earth. The rest of the primals will 
follow when the war is finished. Light send his thanks. Come to our 
coordinates."
 Magnus could not bielieve it. They where winning. He quickly took off to the 
coordinates. Hopeing to find his friend sin good shape.
